Package common

Class RefillOrder

java.lang.Object
gui.ProductControlScreens.TableRefilOrder
common.RefillOrder
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class RefillOrder extends TableRefilOrder implements Serializable
The RefillOrder class represents an order for refilling a vending machine. It extends the TableRefilOrder class and implements the Serializable interface to make it possible to save the object's state. It holds information about the order such as the order ID, product ID, machine ID, creation date, amount at request, new amount, assigned employee and product name.

Ravid & Ben
